      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/12/119",
      "text": [
        " اَلسِّوَاكِ «لاَ تَدَعْهُ فِي كُلِّ ثَلاَثَةِ أَيَّامٍ وَ لَوْ أَنْ تُمِرَّهُ مَرَّةً وَاحِدَةً."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.119 - Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) said about the siwak:\n\"Do not neglect it for more than three days, even if you use it just once.\""
        ]
      }
